line_1: As from hard Rocks rebounds the shatt'ring Wrack,
line_2: Nor thou, that flings me flound'ring from thy Back,

line_1: Burst nature round me in a gen'ral wrack,
line_2: Ye solid poles, give way; ye skies, roll back;

line_1: But how had all his Fortune felt a Wrack,
line_2: Had that false Servant sped in Safety back?
